snippet.title: Show do Milhão 2 (2002) [SEGA Mega Drive Longplay]
snippet.description: Show do Milhão is a Sega Mega Drive game based on a Brazilian TV show with the same name. It was published exclusively in Brazil in 2002 by Tectoy. Show do Milhão Volume 2 is known to be the last game for Mega Drive officially released in any region.
